/cut_event\"><code>cut</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/drag_event\"><code>drag</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/dragend_event\"><code>dragend</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/dragenter_event\"><code>dragenter</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/dragleave_event\"><code>dragleave</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/dragover_event\"><code>dragover</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/dragstart_event\"><code>dragstart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/drop_event\"><code>drop</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/gotpointercapture_event\"><code>gotpointercapture</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/input_event\"><code>input</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/lostpointercapture_event\"><code>lostpointercapture</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/mscandidatewindowhide_event\"><code>mscandidatewindowhide</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/mscandidatewindowshow_event\"><code>mscandidatewindowshow</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/mscandidatewindowupdate_event\"><code>mscandidatewindowupdate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/paste_event\"><code>paste</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"概述","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code>onchange</code>可以用来获取或设置当前元素的<code>change</code>事件的事件处理函数。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"语法","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">element.onchange = 事件处理函数\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"备注","isH3":true,"content":"<p>下面的伪代码演示了，在 Mozilla 中，onchange 事件是如何触发的：</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">  control.onfocus = focus;\n  control.onblur = blur;\n  function focus () {\n      original_value = control.value;\n  }\n\n  function blur () {\n      if (control.value&nbsp;!= original_value)\n        control.onchange();\n  }\n</pre>\n\n<p>因此，如果你在你的 <code>focus</code> 或 <code>blur</code> 事件的处理函数里修改一个控件的值的话，你可能遇到一些关于 <code>change</code> 事件意想不到的现象。另外，<code>change</code> 事件是在 <code>blur</code> 事件发生之后才触发的。这一点和 IE 不同。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"规范","isH3":true,"content":"<p>DOM Level 0 不属于任何标准</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"相关链接","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Events/events.html#Events-eventgroupings-htmlevents\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 2: HTML event types</a></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"onchange可以用来获取或设置当前元素的change事件的事件处理函数。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onchange","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onchange","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/conflicting/web/api/htmlelement/change_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/conflicting/web/api/htmlelement/change_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API","title":"指数"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/HTMLElement/change_event","title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onchange"}],"pageTitle":"GlobalEventHandlers.onchange | MDN","noIndexing":true}}